quran[10{c,v,t}:
58,12,"ae logo jo imaan laaye ho, jab tum rasool se takhlia mein baat karo to baat karne se pehlay kuch sadqa do yeh tumahray liye behtar aur pakeeza tar hai Albata agar tum sadqa dainay ke liye kuch nah pao to Allah ghafoor o Raheem hai"
58,13,"kya tum dar gay is baat se ke takhlia mein guftagu karne se pehlay tumhe sadqat dainay hunge? acha, agar tum aisa nah karo aur Allah ne tum ko is se maaf kar diya to namaz qaim karte raho, zkoh dete raho aur Allah aur is ke rasool ki itaat karte raho tum jo kuch karte ho Allah is se bakhabar hai"
58,14,"kya tum ne dekha nahi unn logon ko jinhon ne dost banaya hai aik aisay giroh ko jo Allah ka maghzoob hai? woh nah tumahray hain nah unn ke, aur woh jaan boojh kar jhooti baat par kasmain khatay hain"
58,15,"Allah ne un ke liye sakht azaab muhayya kar rakha hai, barray hi buray kartoot hain jo woh kar rahay hain"
58,16,"onhon ne apni qasmon ko dhaal bana rakha hai jis ki aarr mein woh Allah ki raah se logon ko roktay hain, iss par un ke liye zillat ka azaab hai"
58,17,"Allah se bachanay ke liye nah un ke maal kuch kaam ayen ge nah un ki aulaad woh dozakh ke yaar hain, isi mein woh hamesha rahen ge"
58,18,"jis roz Allah un sab ko uthaye ga, woh is ke samnay bhi usi terhan kasmain khayen ge jis terhan tumahray samnay khatay hain aur apne nazdeek yeh samjhain ge ke is se un ka kuch kaam ban jaye ga khoob jaan lau, woh parlay darjay ke jhutay hain"
58,19,"shetan unn par musallat ho chuka hai aur a ُs ne khuda ki yaad unn ke dil se bhala di hai woh shetan ki party ke log hain khabardaar ho, shetan ki party walay hi khasaray mein rehne walay hain"
58,20,yaqeenan zaleel tareen makhloqaat mein se hain woh log jo Allah aur is ke rasool ka muqaabla karte hain
58,21,Allah ne likh diya hai ke mein aur mere rasool ghalib ho kar rahen ge fi al waqea Allah zabardast aur zor aawar hai
